00:04:35.310 --> 00:04:36.960
<i>Silence Suzuka!</i>

00:04:35.330 --> 00:04:38.520
{\an9}Silence Suzuka

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:42.100
She's so pretty…

00:04:42.100 --> 00:04:44.290
She was voted most popular among the fans.

00:04:47.640 --> 00:04:49.930
<i>She's the most popular.</i>

00:04:49.930 --> 00:04:51.510
Hmm…

00:04:55.020 --> 00:04:57.650
Those are some nice hind legs…

00:04:57.650 --> 00:05:00.480
A perfect horse girl.

00:05:03.060 --> 00:05:05.560
Wh… Wh-Wh-What are you doing?!

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:09.330
Huh?

00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:11.550
U-Um…

00:05:11.550 --> 00:05:12.980
Are you okay?

00:05:13.410 --> 00:05:14.770
Are you still alive?

00:05:17.110 --> 00:05:18.210
Um…

00:05:18.610 --> 00:05:20.280
Don't worry about it.

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:21.130
I'm used to it.

00:05:21.130 --> 00:05:21.910
Used to it?!

00:05:21.910 --> 00:05:23.830
Where are you from?

00:05:23.830 --> 00:05:24.760
Where were you born?

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:25.830
How old are you?

00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:27.760
What's your weight?

00:05:28.490 --> 00:05:30.630
Y-You're so rude.

00:05:30.630 --> 00:05:32.660
My mom was right!

00:05:32.660 --> 00:05:34.620
The city is full of perverts!

00:05:34.620 --> 00:05:35.730
Perverts?

00:05:35.730 --> 00:05:38.900
You lie to girls, saying you'll
get them a debut, right?

00:05:38.900 --> 00:05:41.760
I'm not interested.

00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:43.070
Bye!

00:05:46.090 --> 00:05:48.220
<i>Welcome to the Twinkle Series!</i>

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:50.760
<i>These races can be enjoyed by all citizens!</i>

00:05:50.760 --> 00:05:52.700
<i>It's a great sport for entertainment.</i>

00:05:52.700 --> 00:05:55.910
<i>Which horse girl will become number one?</i>

00:05:55.910 --> 00:05:57.930
I, Akasaka, will be your host today.

00:05:57.930 --> 00:06:00.040
Analysis will be done by Hosoe-san.

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.830
Welcome today, Hosoe-san.

00:06:01.830 --> 00:06:03.230
Thank you.

00:06:03.230 --> 00:06:05.670
Everyone has their eyes on Silence Suzuka.

00:06:06.110 --> 00:06:09.130
We'll have to see just how she runs today.

00:06:09.130 --> 00:06:12.100
It's time for today's main race.

00:06:23.430 --> 00:06:27.280
I wonder where the number one girl is…

00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:31.240
Looks like it's your first
time seeing a real race.

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:33.180
You're that guy from before…

00:06:33.180 --> 00:06:34.430
It's my first time.

00:06:34.430 --> 00:06:35.670
Is there something wrong with that?

00:06:37.460 --> 00:06:39.120
You left your hometown

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.690
to make your racing debut.

00:06:40.690 --> 00:06:42.100
Does that about sum it up?

00:06:42.100 --> 00:06:46.960
I promised my mom back home that I'd
become the best horse girl in Japan.

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:49.050
So don't get in my way.

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:51.300
Best in Japan, huh?

00:06:51.300 --> 00:06:52.550
That's right.

00:06:54.050 --> 00:06:57.530
So, what does it mean to be the
best horse girl in Japan?

00:06:58.740 --> 00:07:00.920
W-Well…

00:07:05.940 --> 00:07:08.610
<i>They've all jumped beautifully off the line.</i>

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:12.030
<i>Silence Suzuka has quickly taken the lead.</i>

00:07:17.540 --> 00:07:18.790
She's fast.

00:07:18.790 --> 00:07:20.880
Her legwork is wonderful.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:22.040
It's perfect.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:24.080
The advice worked.

00:07:25.250 --> 00:07:28.170
<i>She's passed the 1,000 meter
mark at 57.8 seconds.</i>

00:07:28.170 --> 00:07:30.370
She's taken quite a lead.

00:07:30.370 --> 00:07:32.130
Is this just how she normally runs?

00:07:32.130 --> 00:07:34.020
<i>Or is she going too fast?</i>

00:07:34.020 --> 00:07:36.290
<i>She's all alone!</i>

00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:38.810
You can't always win by taking a large lead.

00:07:39.460 --> 00:07:42.040
I told her to conserve her strength
for the first half of the race.

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:46.320
What is she trying to do?
She's ignoring her trainer's instructions.

00:07:46.320 --> 00:07:47.300
She's taking the fourth turn.

00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:51.740
Will she be able to keep up her speed
and her lead until the finish line?

00:07:51.740 --> 00:07:54.660
They're coming up right behind her.

00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:55.930
We can do it!

00:07:55.930 --> 00:07:56.950
We can get her!

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:01.160
No, we can't!

00:08:16.430 --> 00:08:18.830
<i>Silence Suzuka has won!</i>

00:08:18.830 --> 00:08:21.130
<i>She kept her lead!</i>

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:32.960
Silence Suzuka-san…

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.970
I didn't know there was someone so amazing!

00:08:34.970 --> 00:08:40.580
There aren't many horse girls that can
excite the crowd and make people dream.

00:08:41.050 --> 00:08:43.670
However, with these legs…

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:47.170
I knew you were a pervert!

00:08:47.170 --> 00:08:48.090
Bye!

00:08:48.090 --> 00:08:49.380
Hold on.

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:50.880
You still have more to say?

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:52.390
You're not going to watch?

00:08:52.390 --> 00:08:54.930
She's about to stand on the stage—
a privilege only for the winner.

00:08:56.630 --> 00:08:58.390
The Winning Concert!

00:09:01.930 --> 00:09:04.910
<i>The place for you to share your
happiness with the diligent</i>

00:09:04.910 --> 00:09:06.690
<i>horse girls that have seized victory:</i>

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:10.000
<i>the Winning Concert!</i>

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:13.990
<i>All you fans, please give her your cheers!</i>

00:09:15.780 --> 00:09:19.780
<i>Silence Suzuka will be
center stage today!</i>

00:09:23.250 --> 00:09:28.630
<i>Set out on your run and the scenery
changes through the colors of the rainbow</i>

00:09:28.630 --> 00:09:36.300
<i>Giving light to the hope of dashing
towards the future we'd pictured</i>

00:09:38.580 --> 00:09:42.760
<i>Suzuka-san is so pretty in the spotlight.</i>

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:47.480
<i>Mom, I will never forget
what's happened today!</i>

00:09:48.610 --> 00:09:50.920
But I feel like I've forgotten
about something…

00:09:51.730 --> 00:09:54.190
I forgot about my curfew!

00:10:00.160 --> 00:10:01.780
Excuse me!

00:10:01.780 --> 00:10:03.940
It's Special Week!

00:10:03.940 --> 00:10:05.750
I'm late!

00:10:05.750 --> 00:10:07.340
Excuse me!

00:10:07.340 --> 00:10:09.390
It's Special Week!

