the team I'm on today.

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:43.170
{\an7}Run like the Wind

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:43.170
{\an7}Team Altair

00:13:43.170 --> 00:13:45.720
You're on the same team as Suzuka-san, right?

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:46.380
Yes.

00:13:46.380 --> 00:13:54.520
{\an7}Team Mimoza

00:13:46.380 --> 00:13:54.520
{\an7}For Victory!

00:13:46.780 --> 00:13:49.380
I'm thinking of trying out, too!

00:13:49.380 --> 00:13:53.130
Team Rigil is the strongest in the school!

00:13:53.130 --> 00:13:54.520
I…

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:57.140
I want to take that test, too!

