00:14:32.890 --> 00:14:33.990
R-Right.

00:14:33.990 --> 00:14:36.180
<i>Urara-san looks fast.</i>

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:40.350
Please write your name here to register.

00:14:40.350 --> 00:14:41.310
{\an8}Special Week

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:50.700
{\an7}Fuji Kiseki

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:50.700
{\an8}Maruzensky

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:50.700
{\an9}Taiki Shuttle

00:14:52.220 --> 00:14:54.620
{\an7}T. M. Opera O

00:14:52.220 --> 00:14:54.620
{\an9}Air Groove

00:14:56.060 --> 00:14:58.460
{\an7}Narita Brian

00:14:56.060 --> 00:14:58.460
{\an9}Hishi Amazon

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:02.290
{\an9}Symboli Rudolf

00:15:03.220 --> 00:15:05.770
Spe-chan, time to go!

00:15:05.770 --> 00:15:06.610
Right.

00:15:07.220 --> 00:15:10.260
I wonder if Suzuka-san isn't here.

00:15:10.260 --> 00:15:11.050
Next.

00:15:11.050 --> 00:15:13.270
I want to win in an Open match.

00:15:13.270 --> 00:15:14.130
Next.

00:15:14.130 --> 00:15:16.220
I want to be a successful Rigil member!

00:15:16.220 --> 00:15:17.320
Next.

00:15:18.390 --> 00:15:20.170
Next, Special Week.

00:15:20.170 --> 00:15:21.190
Y-Yes!

00:15:21.190 --> 00:15:22.770
Do you have a goal?

00:15:22.770 --> 00:15:25.140
W-Well…

00:15:26.310 --> 00:15:29.110
I want to be the top horse girl in Japan!

00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:35.420
My mom told me to become the
best horse girl in Japan,

00:15:35.420 --> 00:15:37.970
so that's why I decided to come here!

00:15:57.530 --> 00:16:00.100
The gates aren't as roomy as I expected.

00:16:08.930 --> 00:16:10.330
Are you ready?!

00:16:10.330 --> 00:16:11.740
Here I go!

00:16:16.740 --> 00:16:17.910
I have to run!

00:16:23.750 --> 00:16:25.330
<i>Everyone's so fast!</i>

00:16:25.770 --> 00:16:28.270
So we want El Condor Pasa, huh?

00:16:28.270 --> 00:16:29.420
You're her classmate, right?

00:16:29.420 --> 00:16:30.300
What do you think of her?

00:16:30.300 --> 00:16:32.470
She's in a good position.

00:16:32.470 --> 00:16:34.130
That transfer student…

00:16:35.670 --> 00:16:37.560
Doesn't look like she's
going to be that great.

00:16:45.770 --> 00:16:48.610
<i>It's hard to run on the track…</i>

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:55.990
<i>It's Suzuka-san!</i>

00:17:13.260 --> 00:17:16.220
- Can't keep up!
- Can't keep up!

00:17:19.300 --> 00:17:21.000
Stay away!

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:22.770
What do you want me to do?!

00:17:30.730 --> 00:17:33.230
Why do I have to do this…

00:17:40.850 --> 00:17:41.910
I can do this!

00:17:45.890 --> 00:17:49.170
{\an8}Goal

00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:52.790
<i>I did it, Mom!</i>

00:17:58.510 --> 00:18:00.610
I'm going to work you hard.

00:18:00.610 --> 00:18:02.560
Thank you!

00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:04.520
Huh? I wasn't first?

00:18:08.130 --> 00:18:09.190
Suzuka-san…

00:18:09.190 --> 00:18:11.400
I'm tired!

00:18:11.400 --> 00:18:13.490
{\an8}I'm so tired!

00:18:12.610 --> 00:18:13.940
<i>Suzuka-san…</i>

00:18:16.320 --> 00:18:17.800
Are you serious?

00:18:22.070 --> 00:18:24.240
That was close today!

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:25.290
Yeah.

00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:28.060
Don't give up! Let's keep working at it!

00:18:28.060 --> 00:18:28.920
Yeah.

00:18:28.920 --> 00:18:29.850
See you later.

00:18:30.370 --> 00:18:31.880
Bye.

00:18:40.040 --> 00:18:43.370
I wanted to join Suzuka-san's team.

00:18:49.350 --> 00:18:52.360
{\an9}Team Spica

00:18:49.350 --> 00:18:52.360
{\an8}Join our team

00:18:50.010 --> 00:18:51.560
Spica?

00:18:57.620 --> 00:18:58.610
Huh?

00:19:04.410 --> 00:19:07.140
Scarlet, Vodka…

00:19:07.140 --> 00:19:08.750
Do it!

00:19:09.690 --> 00:19:13.710
You know, there's no point in disguising
yourselves if you're going to say your names.

00:19:15.010 --> 00:19:17.580
Heave ho, heave ho, heave ho…

00:19:17.580 --> 00:19:19.710
<i>Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What's going on?!</i>

00:19:19.710 --> 00:19:23.030
<i>Mom said there were a lot
of dangers in the city!</i>

00:19:23.030 --> 00:19:26.720
<i>I should have eaten more carrots!</i>

00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:29.560
<i>Mom!</i>

00:19:27.450 --> 00:19:29.560
{\an8}We brought her!

00:19:29.560 --> 00:19:30.920
This is the right girl, right?

00:19:30.920 --> 00:19:32.060
Yeah.

00:19:32.450 --> 00:19:35.430
Wh-Where am I?

00:19:36.230 --> 00:19:36.730
Hey.

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:41.950
It's the pervert!

00:19:41.950 --> 00:19:42.750
Pervert?!

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:44.140
No, no, no!

00:19:44.140 --> 00:19:45.210
You misunderstand.

00:19:45.210 --> 00:19:46.870
Call me Trainer.

00:19:47.180 --> 00:19:50.530
T-Trainer-san…

00:19:50.530 --> 00:19:51.660
What?!

00:19:52.070 --> 00:19:54.010
Everyone, introduce yourselves.

00:19:54.730 --> 00:19:57.590
{\an7}Daiwa Scarlet

00:19:54.730 --> 00:19:57.590
Gold Ship

00:19:54.730 --> 00:19:57.590
{\an9}Vodka

00:19:55.300 --> 00:19:57.590
Welcome to Team Spica!

00:19:57.590 --> 00:20:10.890
{\an8}Spica

00:19:57.960 --> 00:19:59.640
Spica?

00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:01.220
You mean that weird sign that was up?!

00:20:01.220 --> 00:20:04.410
You'll be on this team starting today.

00:20:04.410 --> 00:20:07.220
Don't just decide that on your own!

00:20:07.220 --> 00:20:08.610
Oh, but I will.

00:20:08.610 --> 00:20:10.110
I'm going to polish you up.

00:20:10.110 --> 00:20:10.890
What?!

00:20:10.890 --> 00:20:12.490
Even though she was second?

00:20:12.490 --> 00:20:13.140
Yeah.

00:20:13.140 --> 00:20:16.390
Her last three furlongs were
33.8 seconds. That's great.

00:20:16.390 --> 00:20:19.030
She gained her breath back pretty
fast after she was done, too.

00:20:22.920 --> 00:20:24.470
Suzuka-san?!

00:20:25.030 --> 00:20:27.610
Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Why are you here?!

00:20:27.610 --> 00:20:31.190
Suzuka transferred here
from Rigil today, right?

00:20:31.190 --> 00:20:33.000
Yes, that's right.

00:20:33.700 --> 00:20:35.140
Why?!

00:20:35.140 --> 00:20:38.420
That team doesn't understand
how Suzuka-san runs.

00:20:39.890 --> 00:20:44.490
You said it was your goal to become
the best horse-girl in Japan, right?

00:20:44.490 --> 00:20:46.800
I did, but…

00:20:47.210 --> 00:20:49.640
What does it mean to be the
best horse girl in Japan?

00:20:51.350 --> 00:20:52.310
Well…

00:20:52.310 --> 00:20:54.230
To win in G-I, of course.

00:20:54.230 --> 00:20:55.870
The derby for me.

00:20:55.870 --> 00:20:57.370
The Arima Kinen.

00:20:58.090 --> 00:20:59.480
What do you think, Suzuka?

00:21:03.510 --> 00:21:04.600
Dreams.

00:21:04.600 --> 00:21:05.700
Dreams?

00:21:06.980 --> 00:21:11.950
I want to be a horse girl
that can make people dream.

00:21:15.620 --> 00:21:18.460
{\an8}You promised your mom that
you'd become the best in Japan.

00:21:18.460 --> 00:21:21.840
{\an8}I'll help you make your idea
of "best in Japan" into reality.

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:27.580
You're not laughing, Trainer-san.

00:21:27.580 --> 00:21:28.200
Huh?

00:21:28.200 --> 00:21:31.960
I said I wanted to be the best, and you…

00:21:32.770 --> 00:21:36.270
{\an8}I want to do my best on this team.

00:21:36.270 --> 00:21:39.130
{\an8}All right!

00:21:39.130 --> 00:21:39.900
{\an8}<i>And…</i>

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:44.020
{\an8}<i>I want to run with Suzuka-san!</i>

00:21:44.860 --> 00:21:47.000
{\an8}Yeah! We got a member!

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:49.190
{\an8}Now we've got enough people.

00:21:49.190 --> 00:21:52.240
{\an8}We're starting on the
Twinkle Series next week!

00:21:52.240 --> 00:21:53.160
Yeah!

00:21:53.160 --> 00:21:54.810
So what's your name?

00:21:54.810 --> 00:21:56.510
{\an8}Special Week.

00:21:56.510 --> 00:21:57.970
{\an8}Nice to meet you!

00:21:57.970 --> 00:21:59.720
{\an8}Special Week, huh?

00:21:59.720 --> 00:22:01.340
{\an8}I'll register you.

00:22:01.340 --> 00:22:02.610
{\an8}Work hard next week.

00:22:02.610 --> 00:22:03.710
Next week?

00:22:03.710 --> 00:22:07.410
{\an8}Trainer-san, are you thinking of…

00:22:09.190 --> 00:22:11.430
{\an8}Next week, we'll have your debut match!

00:22:13.450 --> 00:22:14.070
What?

00:22:14.810 --> 00:22:15.750
What?

00:22:17.140 --> 00:22:18.130
I'll crush you!

00:22:18.130 --> 00:22:19.350
What?!

00:22:21.530 --> 00:22:25.030
What?!

00:22:30.750 --> 00:22:35.970
Do you hear the fanfare as
we race towards the finish?

00:22:35.970 --> 00:22:42.500
I want to see that shining future with you

00:22:44.550 --> 00:22:50.840
{\an8}Umamusume

00:22:46.420 --> 00:22:50.720
Pretty Derby

00:22:52.730 --> 00:22:58.450
If we just start to run, that's
where our story will begin

00:22:58.450 --> 00:23:03.470
It's always waiting right in front of us

00:23:03.470 --> 00:23:09.080
If you reach out just a little
more, we can seize that glory

00:23:09.080 --> 00:23:15.940
Aim for the top, challenge
them all, and it's off to the races

00:23:16.750 --> 00:23:21.940
Even the goddess of victory will be dazzled

00:23:21.940 --> 00:23:29.220
By your big debut that's just around the bend

00:23:29.220 --> 00:23:34.640
So can you hear the fanfare
as we race towards the finish?

00:23:34.640 --> 00:23:40.110
I want to see that shining future with you

00:23:40.110 --> 00:23:45.620
Let's overtake them all! It's
a track laid out just for you!

00:23:45.620 --> 00:23:53.380
Your dreams are at the finish if you believe

